### CSAP API Doc Example - HTTP Test File
### Use with IntelliJ IDEA HTTP Client or VS Code REST Client extension

@baseUrl = http://localhost:8080
@contentType = application/json

### ========================================
### User Management API
### ========================================

### 1. Get user list
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/users?page=1&pageSize=10
Accept: {{contentType}}

### 2. Search users by keyword
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/users?page=1&pageSize=10&keyword=john
Accept: {{contentType}}

### 3. Get user by ID
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/users/1001
Accept: {{contentType}}

### 4. Create new user
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/users
Content-Type: {{contentType}}

{
  "username": "john_doe",
  "email": "john@example.com",
  "phone": "13800138000",
  "age": 25
}

### 5. Create user with validation (should fail - invalid email)
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/users
Content-Type: {{contentType}}

{
  "username": "jo",
  "email": "invalid-email",
  "phone": "12345",
  "age": 15
}

### 6. Update user
PUT {{baseUrl}}/api/users/1001
Content-Type: {{contentType}}

{
  "username": "john_doe_updated",
  "email": "john.updated@example.com",
  "phone": "13800138001",
  "age": 26
}

### 7. Update user status to LOCKED
PATCH {{baseUrl}}/api/users/1001/status?status=LOCKED
Accept: {{contentType}}

### 8. Update user status to ACTIVE
PATCH {{baseUrl}}/api/users/1001/status?status=ACTIVE
Accept: {{contentType}}

### 9. Delete user
DELETE {{baseUrl}}/api/users/1001
Accept: {{contentType}}

### ========================================
### Product Management API
### ========================================

### 1. Get product list
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/products?page=1&pageSize=10
Accept: {{contentType}}

### 2. Get products with filters
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/products?page=1&pageSize=10&categoryId=1&minPrice=1000&maxPrice=10000&onSale=true
Accept: {{contentType}}

### 3. Get product by ID
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/products/2001
Accept: {{contentType}}

### 4. Create new product
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/products
Content-Type: {{contentType}}

{
  "name": "iPhone 15 Pro",
  "description": "最新款苹果手机，A17 Pro芯片，钛金属边框",
  "price": 7999.00,
  "stock": 100,
  "categoryId": 1,
  "onSale": true
}

### 5. Create product with validation (should fail - negative price)
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/products
Content-Type: {{contentType}}

{
  "name": "",
  "description": "Test",
  "price": -100,
  "stock": -10,
  "categoryId": 1,
  "onSale": true
}

### 6. Update product
PUT {{baseUrl}}/api/products/2001
Content-Type: {{contentType}}

{
  "name": "iPhone 15 Pro Max",
  "description": "升级版",
  "price": 8999.00,
  "stock": 50,
  "categoryId": 1,
  "onSale": true
}

### 7. Update product stock
PATCH {{baseUrl}}/api/products/2001/stock?stock=200
Accept: {{contentType}}

### 8. Delete product
DELETE {{baseUrl}}/api/products/2001
Accept: {{contentType}}

### 9. Batch delete products
DELETE {{baseUrl}}/api/products/batch
Content-Type: {{contentType}}

[2001, 2002, 2003]

### ========================================
### API Documentation Endpoints
### ========================================

### Get API documentation JSON
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/csap/doc
Accept: {{contentType}}

### Access API documentation UI
### Open in browser: {{baseUrl}}/csap-api.html

